---

<Layout 
  title="Desarrollo Web Profesional | Sitios Web Modernos y Escalables"
  description="Servicios de desarrollo web profesional. Creamos sitios web rápidos, seguros y optimizados que impulsan el crecimiento de tu negocio."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-16 md:pt-20">
    <ServiceHero {...heroData} />
    
    <!-- Technologies Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-dark-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
              Tecnologías que
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-400 to-secondary-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                dominamos
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
              Utilizamos las tecnologías más modernas y confiables del mercado
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-8">
            {[
              { name: 'React', color: 'from-blue-400 to-blue-600' },
              { name: 'Vue.js', color: 'from-green-400 to-green-600' },
              { name: 'Astro', color: 'from-orange-400 to-orange-600' },
              { name: 'Node.js', color: 'from-green-500 to-green-700' },
              { name: 'TypeScript', color: 'from-blue-500 to-blue-700' },
              { name: 'Tailwind', color: 'from-cyan-400 to-cyan-600' }
            ].map((tech, index) => (
              <div 
                class="text-center group animate-fade-in"
                style={`animation-delay: ${index * 0.1}s`}
              >
                <div class={`w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r ${tech.color} rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300`}>
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">{tech.name.substring(0, 2)}</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-300 font-medium">{tech.name}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <ServiceBenefits 
      title="Ventajas de nuestro desarrollo web"
      benefits={benefits}
    />
    
    <ProcessSteps steps={processSteps} />

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-dark-950 via-dark-900 to-secondary-950 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-500/10 to-primary-500/10"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            ¿Necesitas un sitio web
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-400 to-primary-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
              de alto rendimiento?
            </span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Nuestro equipo de desarrolladores expertos está listo para crear la solución web perfecta para tu negocio.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
            <a 
              href="/contacto"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-500 to-secondary-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-secondary-500/25 transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105"
            >
              Solicitar presupuesto
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a 
              href="/proyectos"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border border-gray-600 text-gray-300 font-semibold rounded-full hover:border-secondary-500 hover:text-secondary-300 transition-all duration-200"
            >
              Ver proyectos web
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>